            "summary": "On June 5, 2025, HUTCHMED (China) Limited (\u201cHUTCHMED\u201d) (Nasdaq/AIM: HCM; HKEX: 13) and Innovent Biologics, Inc. (\u201cInnovent\u201d) (HKEX: 01801) made a joint announcement from Hong Kong, Shanghai, and Florham Park, N.J. The New Drug Application (\u201cNDA\u201d) for the combination of fruquintinib and sintilimab has been accepted for review by the China National Medical Products Administration (\u201cNMPA\u201d). This combination is intended for the treatment of patients with locally advanced or metastatic renal cell carcinoma who have not responded to previous treatment with one tyrosine kinase inhibitor (\u201cTKI\u201d).",
